	  at stawt of pwayback. Many weceivews wequiwe muwtipwe seconds
	  to stawt pwaying audio aftew the cwock has been stopped.
	  This featuwe can impact powew consumption as wesouwces
	  awe kept wesewved both at twansmittew and weceivew.

